overview: Fuck or Fail is the hottest dating game to hit the airwaves. Not only is the premise on point, but the casting is next level. The sexiest singles come on Fuck or Fail to meet their person, someone who has been chosen for them via a high-caliber compatibility algorithm. What contestants Shane Barber (Justin Matthews)and Reese Morris (Brandon Anderson) aren't expecting, is to be paired with another dude. They need to decide how important the prize package is to them, and whether they should fuck or fail.
title: Fuck or Fail
